+# PHASE 0233-r2 — Data surface EventBus supervisor sources SQL_STORE fix
+
+## Scope
+
+This follow-up fixes the data-surface cell-kind allowlist used by the passive
+supervision helpers introduced by 0233.
+
+The initial 0233 helper `sql_supervision_event(...)` emits the canonical
+`SQL_STORE` cell kind, but the allowlist missed that exact value. The full test
+suite therefore failed before commit while the patch was already applied in the
+working tree.
+
+## Boundary
+
+- no new EventBus
+- no Scheduler.run()
+- no proxy control
+- no SHM mutation
+- no policy decision
+- no GitHub mutation
+- no SQL read/write
+- no Qdrant query/upsert
+- no rehydration execution
+- no pushback execution
+- stdlib only
+
+## Validation
+
+Expected local validation after applying this follow-up on top of the failed
+0233-r1 working tree:
+
+- `python -m compileall -q src tests`
+- `python -m pytest -q tests/rules`
+- `python -m pytest -q`
